1:  Display a vertical pattern in cli.
    Example:
    
    test
    test test
    test test test
    test test test test 
    test test test test test 
    test test test test test test 
    test test test test test
    test test test test
    test test test 
    test test 
    test
    
    
2:  Display a diamond shaped pattern in cli.
    Example:
    
            test
         test test
       test test test
     test test test test 
       test test test
         test test 
            test
            
            
    Alternative example:
            aa
          aaaaaa 
        aaaaaaaaaa
      aaaaaaaaaaaaaa
    aaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaaa    
      aaaaaaaaaaaaaa
        aaaaaaaaaa
          aaaaaa
            aa
            
    (The alternative example circumvents the problem of spacing of a string 
    as pattern).

3:  Display contents of directory
    
    Write a program that asks the user for a directory, and then displays the 
    contents of the directory as a tree.   
    
    
    
        
        

        
        
    
